----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Note on the card images
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
The card illustrations were produced with OpenAI's image model (gpt-image-1.5).
Under OpenAI's terms, output ownership is assigned to the user who generated
them. Be aware that the copyright status of purely AI-generated images is legally
unsettled in some jurisdictions (e.g. the US Copyright Office has held that
wholly machine-generated images may not be copyrightable). This license is
applied by the compiler to the deck as a curated collection — the selection,
arrangement, wordlist, specification, and code — and to the images to the extent
they are protectable. It expresses the author's intent for how the work may be
used regardless of the underlying images' copyright status.
